{
  "id": "RAW_1775ba95",
  "title": "收藏没停过，学习没用过？三个工具提取视频文案变知识库和选题库！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNzYzODgwNw==&mid=2247495407&idx=1&sn=78d5ca8bf39b9289b4df6f1ad0d45dc6",
  "date": "2025-12-23 04:08:00",
  "author": "阿真Irene",
  "siteName": "阿真Irene",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:10px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4203703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/HibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL0hmplkCLhwXxHU09YJdHk8IvC8eBfIgljVm5bCntSvFHRHIZ0RiaoiaQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"558\" data-cropsely2=\"234\" data-imgfileid=\"100011735\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c2e86336&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL0hmplkCLhwXxHU09YJdHk8IvC8eBfIgljVm5bCntSvFHRHIZ0RiaoiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗨大家好！我是阿真！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天分享一个免费AI工具+两套工作流，用于快速提取视频内容和文案分析的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近和朋友聊到，看到很棒的视频就想收藏，收藏从未停止，行动从未开始，就算把视频文案提取了也发挥不出价值，我们也就看一看做点笔记，总不可能去抄袭去洗稿吧。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后我想到一个方式，以文案提取为起点，用一套方法，把这个提取的内容作为一个点去拓展开来，把从这里学到的知识作为起点，延伸出自己的学习和选题思路。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么接下来，我就分享这个视频提取工具和我的思路以及多维表格模板给到大家，希望大家从中获得一些灵感，发散出更多适合自己的进阶之路！</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 音视频文案提取</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先推荐一个很棒的工具，为我们做一些主流平台的视频文案提取。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是我自己常用的工具，它是一个飞书多维表格模板，核心功能完全免费，因为是飞书多维表格官方的模板，在内容的安全和隐私性方面也是非常有保障的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">粘贴视频链接就能自动提取逐字稿和智能摘要。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上链接👉&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://xurl.run/Ze9c3E\" target=\"_blank\">https://xurl.run/Ze9c3E</a></span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">建议在网页端使用，适合的平台非常多，抖音、B站、小红书等等都可以尝试，试过就知道可不可以了🐶本地的视频和音频也可以提取文案👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5268518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00c8a556&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL06fteGmsZD7DXIboOt8AEf5ROrHFOXKaAIFcicnWzVWWzW1LHMj24ow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">操作方式非常简单，复制视频链接，选择平台，然后提交即可。等一小会儿之后，会看到右边的【摘要】和【文案】列都已经生成了内容，点击最右蓝色的【查看详情】就可以查看提取的文案详情内容了👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5296296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c379c2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL2gSRZee1TbicTc8eK74DfwSFich9YZtgLRe9sgV6cfMz1OZjUfL9iaksw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">点击查看详情以后，就可以看到下方的完整的表格内容，包括了从这个链接所提取的视频的摘要以及完整版的文案👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50ccb4d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLgZ53VLl2eWDZdbHvfW6Rh1J69MWsgib94ic2C4sl0iap74uGTSN37WiclA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">文案下方还有一段内容，表头的名称分别是【结果】和【预览链接】。结果这里的内容不用管，它的功能就是把一段文字内容，做成一个“像 Notion 一样好看的网页阅读页”👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=edcf3137&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLqrbibgRzlJPFeS0CwAibtRCRG6vNjCXygjcW4eMJ2jOXa3b5Z7mdcHUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【结果】会把原本的内容原样保留，通过 HTML 和 CSS 进行结构整理与视觉排版，将长段口语内容拆分为清晰的段落，用标题、引用块、高亮和分割线标出重点与层次，并模拟 Notion 风格的版式与阅读体验，使文章在浏览器中更易读、更有层次、更舒服，但内容观点、表达方式和信息密度基本不变。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我们点击【结果】下方的【预览链接】的链接之后，就可以看到排版清晰的的上方文案的网页阅读页了👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21a834cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL9J6XvFS0kDYrr32fvuzLSBzDtGjo1Opf497zXEcMlpZibLt39oqFkTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外，也可以通过本地文件上传的方式去提取音视频的文案👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91fd95a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL4hSMrgE7INHPfrFug2mkLUDC8Q6PkxDIf2AdFUn4YykZEenL3ej35Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个工具简单来说就是，平时刷到不错的课程、播客、直播回放，想学但没时间从头看完的，或者想研究对标账号、拆解爆款，但反复回放手动记录又太费时间的，用这个飞书多维表格模板，粘贴视频链接进去，它会自动提取完整逐字稿，还会生成一份智能摘要告诉你每部分讲了什么。一小时的视频几分钟就能提炼重点。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">好工具的标准很简单：免费、好用、不折腾。这个工具都做到了。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 收藏了，然后呢</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来我要说的是，我们获得了文字内容，然后呢？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">提取是起点，不是终点。终点是我们自己有收获，我们自己能输出。如果把搜集素材当成努力，那只是在感动自己。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">还是使用飞书多维表格，我这里自己做了2个表格，一个适合用于学习文案中的内容，进行知识萃取和知识点延伸；还有一个适合通过学习创作者的创作方向、内容和选题，去进行一个选题的裂变和更多方向的灵感的发散。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;background-color: rgb(106, 93, 245);margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-end;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 5px;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:20px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.1</span></em></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;border-left: 4px solid rgb(106, 93, 245);flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: stretch;height: auto;padding: 5px 10px 0px;background-color: rgba(234, 231, 255, 0.41);border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">知识萃取工厂</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们在各个平台都会刷到一些很有趣的知识和干货，当时看完了又担心过眼就忘，就可以把这个链接保存下来，放到上一步的音视频文案提取工具中，获得文案后，再存到下面的表格里。既做到了内容的收藏，又可以去拓展更多的知识，把别人讲的内容变成自己真正理解、融会贯通的知识。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">表格模板链接我会放在本文最后。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?