   <p style=\"text-align: justify;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">选题裂变工厂</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">选题裂变工厂很适合创作者，可以通过从别人的爆款或者潜力内容中去挖掘出属于自己的选题。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里以@epcdiy 的《为什么说弹窗是Mac对付流氓软件的杀手锏？》举例。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">模板链接我会放在本文最后。还是和之前一样。首先也是复制文案到表格模板的【完整文案】列。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5481481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1d1a2ccf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLRcgFdUgpvr6oxQNj6Z6zzGAmevvemXsiclRjXwYdSAOF6sDIX7iaicasA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面是选题思路：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">选题提炼：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">这个视频在围绕什么观点讲什么内容。这个不需要很详细，比如主要分析核心选题、目标人群和选题类型👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24537037037037038\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58be656b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLODI3FUotoLgAF3JVGyg8kf6Ne5ILSPIyaZkvRicls1TZlafr7VBmkicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">选题延伸：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">一个爆款裂变出五个新选题。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来就是AI基于这个原有的选题，给我们更多新的选题的发散。比如说观众看了这个之前他需要了解什么，以及观众看完之后，下一步可能会想看什么？还有如果我要反驳和质疑这个观点，我又可以做什么方向的内容？以及如果把这个大的选题拆成小的选题，有哪些细分的方向可以再做一期？这是比较垂直深挖的一个方向，再有就是如果我们去跨场景，同样的方法换一个人群或者是平台或者是场景，那么又可以如何去做选题？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面就是对于选题方向的一些推荐，以及对切入点的说明。👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3537037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1622805&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLyQf6NicZFic4KZqCnO3PgfZGrYgJnqbU74BVHicaMyvljl9xt8OKuniadg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">可复用元素：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">哪些句式、结构可以迁移，内容之间它是用什么方式去衔接的，可以去提炼句式，以及有哪些表达是值得我们学习的和有哪些金句可以进行摘录。还有节奏的技巧，就是在哪里它加快或者放慢的节奏。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在不同类型的选题中，可复用元素都是不同的，我们可以从中学到很多。比如可以看看下面这个观点型和故事型两个选题的对比👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7870370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8bc9f499&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLL2nZIBBKic02lfuzHkic15wl8EdT7tn3fubdiaXsQmWZrqctNEjCac6kQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.787962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd0ae94d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSLGhcatpViakRFDHiakTNLxJa6rgoFy8WWQ0JjibEDibAia0aBTS6FeDwnocg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">差距机会点：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">别人没讲透的地方，就是我们创作者的机会。这个选题有什么角度还没有被讲到？或者换一个人群换个角度讲同样的事情，可以怎样去切入？以及作者在哪些地方讲的还不够深，如果要深度地去解析，我还可以从哪些方向去进行补充？以及我有什么相关的经历案例和踩坑，可以和大家分享呢？</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.275\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dcc848c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiafczY6eOdcbx0XIPGa5zSSL7EHicSVnDPID7cI4NmLllDibFFpxMVhibSMCMichIhGubHniaESvzoiaoZ8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外还有脚本结构拆解等等，这里也不过多展开了。有需要还可以添加飞书多维表格自动化等功能，直接将内容推送给自己。大家感兴趣也可以自行去添加和修改，这里我起到一个抛砖引玉的作用。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小结</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-bottom: 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:medium;flex-flow:row;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;background-color:rgba(200, 196, 248, 0.24);border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(200, 196, 248);padding:16px 16px 10px;margin:10px 0px;display:flex;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;justify-content:flex-start;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 1 auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all;font-size:100%;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-light;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">链接分享：</span></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【强烈推荐】一键获取全网音视频逐字稿工具链接👉&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://xurl.run/Ze9c3E\" target=\"_blank\">https://xurl.run/Ze9c3E</a></span></span></strong></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">知识萃取工厂模板链接👉&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://ai.feishu.cn/wiki/Fyh5w4qs3ib6tFk9sJTcCyxdnBb?from=from_copylink\" target=\"_blank\">https://ai.feishu.cn/wiki/Fyh5w4qs3ib6tFk9sJTcCyxdnBb?from=from_copylink</a></span></span></strong></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">选题裂变工厂模板链接👉&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://ai.feishu.cn/wiki/JevnwyvwniOEG2k0fJVcEnKgnth?from=from_copylink\" target=\"_blank\">https://ai.feishu.cn/wiki/JevnwyvwniOEG2k0fJVcEnKgnth?from=from_copylink</a></span></span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">朋友们，与其收藏内容，不如现在就打开链接用起来，行动永远比收藏更有收获哦！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">好啦，以上就是今天全部的内容，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果觉得内容对你有帮助，欢迎猛猛三连鼓励阿真，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">如果有更多想法和思路，欢迎留言，我们可以在评论区一起探讨。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下期见～！</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章介绍了一款免费 AI 工具和两套基于飞书多维表格的工作流，帮助用户将视频内容转化为结构化知识库和可裂变的选题库。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章介绍了一款免费 AI 工具和两套基于飞书多维表格的工作流，帮助用户将视频内容转化为结构化知识库和可裂变的选题库。",
  "summary": "作者分享了如何利用一个免费的音视频文案提取工具，将抖音、B 站、小红书等平台视频以及本地音视频的文案快速提取，并生成智能摘要。在此基础上，文章重点介绍了两套创新的飞书多维表格工作流：一是“知识萃取工厂”，旨在通过 AI 快捷字段分析、底层原理追问、知识关联映射等步骤，将视频内容转化为个人深度理解的知识体系；二是“选题裂变工厂”，针对创作者，通过提炼选题、延伸选题、分析可复用元素和发现差距机会点，帮助从现有爆款内容中挖掘和拓展新选题。文章强调“提取是起点，不是终点”，鼓励读者将收集到的素材转化为自己的产出。",
